HEADWORD: Ubiquitous
<hw>U*biq"ui*tous</hw> <pr>(⟦usl⟧*b⟦icr⟧k"w⟦icr⟧*t⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Ubiquity</er>.]</ety> <def>Existing or being
everywhere, or in all places, at the same time; omnipresent.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>U*biq"ui*tous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In this sense is he <qex>ubiquitous</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>R. D.
